#Help package program:
  package <mode> <...>
# All modes of the package program:
   package new    <name>
+  creates a new package
   package add    <package> <file>
+  adds a file to an existing package
   package erase  <package> <file>
+  removes a file from an existing package
   package remove <package>
+  deletes a package
   package list
+  list of all packages
   package info   <package>
+  list of all files in an existing package
# server-packages:
   package send   <id> <package>
+  sends a package to a server
   package pull   <id/host> <package>
+  receive a package from a server
# server-packages remote mode:
   package remote list <id/host>
+  list of all packages on the server
   package remote remove <id/host> <package>
+  deletes a package from the server
# dowonloaded packages:
   package downloads
+  list of all downloaded packages
